						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in a rice field 4 furlongs to the east of the village.</p>						

						<p>Damaged and worn out. It mentions Chōḷa-mahārāju and Puṇyakumāra. Other details are not known. In characters of 7th-8th century A.D.</p>						

